{"tid":1361607,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教 你 搭 輕 鐵","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T15:58:20.000Z","uid":270154,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"32a6b5f79ce2079c54697c3a100238dfc6ecbe6c","tid":1361607,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">元朗輕鐵分別有四條線<br />\n<br />\n<del>761P 往天逸</del><br />\n615 往屯門碼頭<br />\n610 往屯門碼頭<br />\n614 往屯門碼頭<br />\n<br />\n除左761P之外，其餘三線都經<strong>兆康西鐵站</strong>，<strong>見到即上</strong>。<br />\n如果真係覺得月台好熱，要上<strong>761P</strong>，就去到<strong>坑尾村</strong>落車，轉<strong>751</strong>，一個站就到<strong>天水圍西鐵站</strong>。<br />\n（站名留意輕鐵車內廣播即可，好大聲的。）<br />\n<br />\n其次，<br />\n輕鐵單程票有效時間為兩小時（比較難買定）各位上車前記得買飛。<br />\n<br />\n否則不幸遇上查票員會罰$290大元。<br />\n（購票機同地鐵只係大同小異）</div>"},{"pid":"8009136ddf5ba8f6bf1c5a1dfa4f8ff498c14e83","tid":1361607,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"開錯台sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f738d34f4fd60ed9a2fa02e1f0c100c004fe7fa0","tid":1361607,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d711742c4837b6344f561d24be96eee77b25b4e","tid":1361607,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1dd810aba8cc22ec04a8941f699c2e25da41584","tid":1361607,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d38379bbac3c405706af3085780c834ec4dbd828","tid":1361607,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3e0e43242c9d8043096c79d979b0f0e3367a609","tid":1361607,"uid":270154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcffef5be99bfde92c62d3377aefee14a873756d","tid":1361607,"uid":270